            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#并非所有人都适合吃豆制品#】当豆浆加热到80℃-90℃时，就会产生大量泡沫，很多人误以为豆浆已经煮熟了，但实际上#喝假沸的豆浆可能会中毒#[吃惊] 而大...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%9E%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E5%90%83%E8%B1%86%E5%88%B6%E5%93%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%9E%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E5%90%83%E8%B1%86%E5%88%B6%E5%93%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#并非所有人都适合吃豆制品#</span></a>】当豆浆加热到80℃-90℃时，就会产生大量泡沫，很多人误以为豆浆已经煮熟了，但实际上<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%96%9D%E5%81%87%E6%B2%B8%E7%9A%84%E8%B1%86%E6%B5%86%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%96%9D%E5%81%87%E6%B2%B8%E7%9A%84%E8%B1%86%E6%B5%86%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E6%AF%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#喝假沸的豆浆可能会中毒#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 而大豆中嘌呤较高，痛风人群应少吃豆制品，老人和小孩也不适宜直接吃“豆”👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视一套） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4971177974628369" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视频的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/007S2YvRly1hk4t2beau4j30m80ciwlh.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/LBcLsCi2lx08aojGUP3i01041200pxld0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=864x486.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700860382&amp;ssig=g0wL9UCZwW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/YyGOWvY1lx08aojGEl7y01041200jBgV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700860382&amp;ssig=eol8Gmf8mE&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/5y0XTVbglx08aojGEIGs01041200cmQb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700860382&amp;ssig=m60EHS3TDY&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4971177974628369" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
